---
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  id="top"
  title="moriken web"
  description="もりけんのポートフォリオサイトです。"
>
  <main>
    <Header />
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-5 pt-96 md:px-10">
      <Card>
        <div class="justify-center md:flex">
          <div
            class="flex max-w-[1040px] flex-col gap-32 p-8 md:px-32 md:py-20"
          >
            <section class="items-center justify-center gap-32 md:flex">
              <img class="max-w-[12rem] md:max-w-[18rem]" src="/img/kimi.png" />
              <div>
                <div class="my-8">
                  <div
                    class="mb-3 font-emphasis text-5xl font-bold text-emphasis md:text-6xl"
                  >
                    Kenryu Mori
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="mb-3 font-emphasis text-[1.7rem] font-bold md:text-3xl"
                  >
                    Graduate Student / Software Engineer
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-end gap-6">
                    <a
                      class="inline-block"
                      href="https://github.com/kimisuke0503"
                      ><img
                        class="max-w-[2.5rem]"
                        src="/img/icon-github.webp"
                      /></a
                    >
                    <a class="inline-block" href="https://twitter.com/moriken53"
                      ><img class="max-w-[2.2rem]" src="/img/icon-x.webp" /></a
                    >
                    <a
                      class="inline-block"
                      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kenryu-mori-197765294/"
                      ><img
                        class="max-w-[2.7rem]"
                        src="/img/icon-linkedin.webp"
                      /></a
                    >
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p>
                    I major in information engineering at Osaka Metropolitan
                    University.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    I'm interested in software development and work as intern at
                    Next Finance Tech, Inc.
                  </p>
                  <p class="font-bold">
                    The icon is my beloved cat in Hiroshima (my hometown).
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section>
              <div class="section-title">Work/Education History</div>
              <div class="section-content">
                <ul class="w-[60rem]">
                  <li class="history-li">
                    <div class="history-li-title-wrap">
                      <div class="history-li-title">
                        Rresent<br /> | <br />Apr. 2022
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="history-li-description">
                      Master of Informatics, Osaka Metropolitan University.<br
                      />Software Engineer (internship) at Next Finance Tech,
                      Inc.
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="history-li">
                    <div class="history-li-title-wrap">
                      <div class="history-li-title">
                        Mar. 2022<br /> | <br />Apr. 2018
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="history-li-description">
                      Bachelor of Engineering, Osaka Prefecture University.
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="history-li">
                    <div class="history-li-title-wrap">
                      <div class="history-li-title">
                        Mar. 2018<br /> | <br />May. 1999
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="history-li-description">
                      in Mihara and Onomichi, Hiroshima.
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section>
              <div class="section-title">Interest</div>
              <div class="section-content">
                <p>
                  AWS cloud/Web development/Serverless architecture/Software
                  solution with hardware
                </p>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section>
              <div class="section-title">Academic Paper</div>
              <div class="section-content">
                <ul class="md:mx-28">
                  <li>
                    Seiki Ubukata, Kenryu Mouri and Katsuhiro Honda, &quot;Basic
                    Consideration of Collaborative Filtering Based on Rough
                    Co-clustering Induced by Multinomial Mixture Models &quot;
                    in Proc of International Conference on Soft Computing and
                    Intelligent Systems and 23rd International Symposium on
                    Advanced Intelligent Systems (SCIS&ISIS), Dec. 2022.
                  </li>
                  <br />
                  <li>
                    毛利憲竜, 生方誠希, 本多克宏,
                    "粒状性を考慮したラフ集合ベースの
                    混合多項分布型共クラスタリングに基づく協調フィルタリング",
                    第 39 回ファジィシステムシンポジウム(FSS2023 軽井澤)
                    講演論文集 2B4-1 , 2023年 9月.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section>
              <div class="section-title">Experience</div>
              <div class="section-content">
                <p>AWS-cdk/React/Nextjs/Astrojs/TailwindCSS</p>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Card>
    </section>
    <Footer />
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  section {
    @apply md:ml-10;
  }
  .section-title {
    @apply text-4xl md:text-5xl;
  }
  .section-content {
    @apply flex justify-center py-2 md:py-16;
  }
  .history-li {
    @apply flex border-b-2 py-8;
  }
  .history-li-title-wrap {
    @apply w-1/4 p-3;
  }
  .history-li-title {
    @apply text-center;
  }
  .history-li-description {
    @apply m-auto w-3/4 p-3;
  }
</style>
